<lb n="0080a22"/><head type="no">No. 934</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0080a23"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0080003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本</note>佛說無量功德陀羅尼經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0080a24"/>
<lb n="0080a25"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0080004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔西天譯經〕－【宋】【元】，（宋）＋西【明】</note><app n="0080004"><lem>西天譯經</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">宋西天譯經</rdg></app>三藏<note n="0080005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（朝散…臣）十三字＝（法師）二字【宋】【元】</note><app n="0080005" word-count="13"><lem>朝散大夫試光
<lb n="0080a26"/>祿卿明教大師臣</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">法師</rdg></app>法賢奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0080a27"/><p>爾時世尊告阿難言。汝當諦聽我今為汝及
<lb n="0080a28"/>末法眾生。宣說無量功德陀羅尼。汝當憶念
<lb n="0080a29"/>勿得忘失。使<note n="0080006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">於＝于【明】＊</note><app n="0080006"><lem>於</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">于</rdg></app>當來濁惡世中。與諸眾生作
<pb ed="T" id="T19.0934.0080b" n="0080b"/>
<lb n="0080b01"/>大善利。阿難若有眾生得聞此陀羅尼。每日
<lb n="0080b02"/>晨朝誦二十一遍。是人<app type="＊" source="0080006"><lem>於</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">于</rdg></app>千劫中所積惡業
<lb n="0080b03"/>悉皆消滅。見身獲得安隱快樂。若人<note n="0080007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">志＝至【元】【明】</note><app n="0080007"><lem>志</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">至</rdg></app>心持
<lb n="0080b04"/>誦一洛叉數。是人當來得見慈氏菩薩。若持
<lb n="0080b05"/>誦二洛叉數。當來得見觀自在菩薩。若持誦
<lb n="0080b06"/>三洛叉數。當來得見無量壽佛。即說陀羅尼
<lb n="0080b07"/>曰</p>
<lb n="0080b08"/><p type="dharani">那謨<note place="inline">引</note>囉怛那<note place="inline">二合</note>怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>夜<note place="inline">引</note>野<note place="inline">一</note>那莫阿<note place="inline">引</note>
<lb n="0080b09"/>哩也<note place="inline">二合</note>阿彌多<note place="inline">引</note><note n="0080008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">婆＝媻【明】＊</note><app n="0080008"><lem>婆</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">媻</rdg></app><note place="inline">引</note>野<note place="inline">二</note>怛他<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00344;多<note place="inline">引</note>野
<lb n="0080b10"/><note place="inline">三</note>阿囉曷<note place="inline">二合</note>帝<note place="inline">引</note>三藐訖三<note place="inline">二合</note>沒馱<note place="inline">引</note>野<note place="inline">四</note>怛
<lb n="0080b11"/>&CB00853;他<note place="inline">引五</note>阿彌帝<note place="inline">引六</note>阿彌&CB00418;<note place="inline">引</note>訥<app type="＊" source="0080008"><lem>婆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">媻</rdg></app><note place="inline">二合</note>味
<lb n="0080b12"/><note place="inline">引七</note>阿彌多三<app type="＊" source="0080008"><lem>婆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">媻</rdg></app>味<note place="inline">八</note>阿彌多尾訖蘭<note place="inline">二合引</note>帝
<lb n="0080b13"/><note place="inline">引九</note>阿彌多尾訖蘭<note place="inline">二合引</note>多&CB00344;<note place="inline">引</note>彌&CB00135;<note place="inline">十</note>&CB00344;&CB00344;
<lb n="0080b14"/>那計<note place="inline">引</note>哩底<note place="inline">二合</note>羯哩<note place="inline">引十一</note>薩哩&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>訖梨
<lb n="0080b15"/><note place="inline">二合</note>舍<note place="inline">十二</note>剎煬羯哩<note place="inline">二合</note>曳<note place="inline">引</note>娑&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合引</note>賀<note place="inline">引十
<lb n="0080b16"/>三</note></p>
<lb n="0080b17"/><p>爾時阿難。得聞如來說是無量功德陀羅尼
<lb n="0080b18"/>已。歡喜信受禮佛而退</p>
<lb n="0080b19"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead>佛說無量功德陀羅尼經</jhead></juan></div1>
